            {
                "comment": "Really enjoyed this class. The class was easy up until the final RETScreen project which took up a TON of time at the end of the semester. Really interesting content though and would suggest this class to anyone interested in the environment or renewable energy technology.",
                "difficulty_rating": 2,
                "quality_rating": 4
            },
            {
                "comment": "Class is online in the spring, so I only saw his video lectures. His teaching was okay, but the lectures were long and it was hard to focus. Online quizzes weren't bad. Beware: if you aren't in engineering and are in env. studies (like me), this is harder than you think it will be, but it's manageable. Projects are a pain.",
